                                "text": " is same as a newline right?"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "rich_text_section",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "Exactly. I find it convenient in some one-liners, like (random example from one of the AoC solutions) "
